      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: payment, refund, dispute + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'payment' → Airtable · ②→ Handle 'refund' → Forward API · ③→ Handle 'dispute' → Forward API · ④→ Log Unrecognized Kind",
